quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,62,"Anndu gom…óin…ďe …ďen ko …ďen gom…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ďe laatike hi…ďe wonndi e makko e dow fiyaake moftu…óo, …ďe yahatah haa …ďe duŇčinoo e makko, pellet, …ďen …óa…ď…ďiray…ďe ma duŇčayee ko …ďen …óon woni gom…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ďe …óa…ď…ďirii ma duŇčayee fii yoga e fiyaake ma…ď…ďe, duŇčano on mo yi…óu…óaa [duŇčanaade] e ma…ď…ďe, insinano…óaa …ďe ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,63,"Wata on wa…óu noddugol Nulaa…óo on hakkunde moo…óon wano noddugol yoga e moo…óon yoga. Gom…óii Alla no Anndi …ďen sortotoo…ďe e moo…óon e moltagol, …ďen wonu…ďe lunndaade yamaruyee makko on, yo …ďe rento fii wata fitina hi…ďu …ďe maa…óum Lempte muusu…óe he…ďa …ďe"
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla heeranii ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi gom…óii hiMo Anndi ko wonu…óon e hoore mu'un kon, √Ďalnde …ďe ruttetee faade ka Makko O yeetoo …ďe ko …ďe gollunoo kon. Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  25,1,Mawnii On Jippin…óo Serndoore nden e dow jeyaa…óo Makko on fii yo wonan winndire nden jertinoowo
  25,2,"On Mo woodanii …óum Laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, o jogitaaki …ďi…ó…óo laatanaaki Mo kadi kafidaa…óo ka Laamu. O tagii kala huunde O e…ď…ďindiinde e e…ď…ďugol"
